)BODY Expand(//)
%Tutorial /-/  EDIT  /-/ Tutorial
%COMMAND ===>_ZCMD                                                             +
+
%                     -----------------------------------
                      |      Edit Macro  "RESUME"       |
                      -----------------------------------
+
%FUNCTION :+This Edit macro allows a user to restore a member edit from the
            last saved copy. This can be used when you have made a change you
            did not mean to make.
%SYNTAX :+  RESUME
            RESUME HELP or H
%NOTE :+    Not allowed on PS files (you must do it yourself).
+
)PROC
  &ZCONT = PAJTRSM
)END
